&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://dinersclubofferstool.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/06/APAC-NEW-DELHI-LE-CIRQUE-OFFER-LOGO-MEDIUM.jpg&quot;&gt;&lt;img class=&quot;alignnone size-full wp-image-4391&quot; src=&quot;http://dinersclubofferstool.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/06/APAC-NEW-DELHI-LE-CIRQUE-OFFER-LOGO-MEDIUM.jpg&quot; alt=&quot;APAC- NEW DELHI- LE CIRQUE- OFFER- LOGO MEDIUM&quot; width=&quot;125&quot; height=&quot;72&quot; /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Although the original circus theme d&eacute;cor is absent, the classic&nbsp;Le Cirque signature dishes remain. In an elegant dining room on the 10&lt;sup&gt;th&lt;/sup&gt; floor of The Leela Palace, diners can experience the magic of the Le Cirque mystique. Having been named the &lt;strong&gt;Best European Restaurant (in a 5-star) at the Timeout Food Awards 2014&lt;/strong&gt;, the French Italian menu will delight and service is charming and polished. An al fresco terrace is perfect for dining with a beautiful view of the skyline. Formal or smart casual attire.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Contact the restaurant by phone at +91 11 3933 1390 or by email at &lt;a href=&quot;mailto:lecirque.newdelhi@theleela.com&quot;&gt;lecirque.newdelhi@theleela.com&lt;/a&gt; to book your reservation&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Mention Diners Club International Privileges Dining Collection to receive your special benefit&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Provide your name, date you would like to dine, number of guests, preferred time, cell phone or local (hotel) phone number and email address. If making a reservation by email, please write&nbsp;&lsquo;Le Cirque Reservation&rsquo; as the email subject&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Cancellation Policy: As a courtesy, if you are unable to attend your dinner please call the restaurant to cancel your reservation&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Reconfirmation Policy: The restaurant will call the number you provided by 18:00 on the day of your reservation to reconfirm&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;TERMS &amp;amp; CONDITIONS&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Follow booking instructions to ensure receiving your Privileges Dining Collection amenity&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Based on availability at the time of booking&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;A main course must be purchased to receive your dining benefit&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Your Privileges Dining Collection benefit may not be combined with other offers&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Fulfillment of the odffer is the sole responsibility of the participating&nbsp;Diners Club International&nbsp;Restaurant Merchant&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Restaurant participation and benefits are subject to change or cancellation without notice&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

